<section id="why-trust-us" class="py-20 px-6 bg-base-100 border-t border-base-300 text-base-content">
	<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
		<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-6">Why Homeowners Call Us First</h2>
		<p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
			We’re a local, licensed, family-run contractor — not a franchise — with a reputation for doing things right.
		</p>
		<div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-4 text-left">
			<div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Licensed & Local</h3>
				<p>We handle permits, follow code, and carry full insurance. No shortcuts. No subcontractors. Just solid work done the right way.</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Flat-Rate Pricing</h3>
				<p>Clear pricing with fast and affordable replacements. No salesman. No commissions. No pressure. No surprise fees.</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Reliable & Respectful</h3>
				<p>We show up on time, work efficiently, and leave no mess. Most installs are done in a few hours.</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Top Brands & Warranties</h3>
				<p>We install Rheem and Bradford White water heaters with a <span class="font-semibold">2-year labor warranty</span>, full manufacturer coverage, and optional extended protection.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
